==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Catbird
<hw>Cat"bird</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An
American bird (<spn>Galeoscoptes Carolinensis</spn>), allied to the
mocking bird, and like it capable of imitating the notes of other birds,
but less perfectly. Its note resembles at times the mewing of a
cat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

